true_child = PandasNode('True Node')
false_child = PandasNode('False Node')
head = PandasNode('Node', lambda df: df['vals'] > 5, pd.DataFrame(np.matrix
    (range(10)).T, columns=['vals']), true_child, false_child)
tree = PandasBDT(head)
tree.execute()
leaves = tree.get_leaves()
index_true_leave = leaves[0].data_frame.index.tolist()
index_false_leave = leaves[-1].data_frame.index.tolist()
assert (index_true_leave == range(6, 10) and index_false_leave == range(6)
    ) == True
